** About us **

Tektalent has partnered with a technology service provider that is taking the
Australian market by storm. Our client offers a plethora of unique benefits &
attractive notions to put them in a unique position of offering Managed
services with a difference. Our client is genuinely dedicated to keeping the
culture & morale of the team happy & fulfilled, whilst offering an environment
to support customers with the latest & most innovative technology stacks. This
role is permanent & offers a flexible working environment to allow you the
freedom to work from the office, or from the comfort of your own home. If you
are stuck in a repetitive or mundane managed services environment where every
day is the same, we can assure you that our client will change your
perspective & give you a fresh new lease on working for a technology service
provider, that genuinely cares about you & their customers.

** Qualifications & experience **

  * Technical troubleshooting experience in: Cloud services, Virtualization, Networking, Windows environments, Remote desktop, Security, device management, desktop support, backup, firewalls, system administration, systems engineering 
  * Excellent customer service ability & drive to offer our customer's a communicative, informed & enjoyable experience 
  * 3 + years' experience providing technical / IT support 
  * Self-motivated & passion for technology / Customer service 
  * Strong communication skills & ability to relate to people 
  * Having experience working within an MSP environment is highly attractive but desirable 

** Tasks & responsibilities **

  * Act as an escalation point to the level 1 engineers, mentor & lead the way in resolving tickets & incidents 
  * Maintain ticket queues & updating clients on progress 
  * Deploy & manage cloud-based tools using M365 & Intune 
  * Focus on customer satisfaction, solve complex problems, tailor solutions to meet customer needs, communicating strongly & with empathy 
  * Support, deploy, manage, oversee & monitor systems, software & infrastructure 
  * Engage in complex troubleshooting of client environments & being the liaison between the business & client's 

** Benefits **

  * Join one of Australia's leading Technology Success providers, taking managed services to the next echelon of service 
  * Join a business offering a model beyond a standard MSP, offering the enrichment of technology through digital advisory, IT strategy, cloud computing, cyber security, unified communications & connectivity 
  * Dedicated to adapting to innovation & being ahead of the curve, which allows you to have a genuine roadmap for growth & long term tenure 
  * Culture of "Better together" & "celebrating success" 
  * Flexible work arrangements / Hybrid / ability to work from home 
  * Learning & development is taken seriously 
  * One of the best break-out areas to let your hair down with onsite arcade / DJ / Games area 
  * A leadership team that genuinely cares about your wellbeing & happiness 
  * Exciting time to join a business that is thriving, experiencing hyper growth, & dedicated to not being just another standard MSP 

Tektalent is on a mission to set the standard for how recruitment should be
done, we look forward to reviewing your application.

